<Layout 
  title="About Goan Traders - Your Trusted Building Materials Supplier Since Years" 
  description="Learn about Goan Traders, your reliable cement and building materials supplier in Goa. Authorized dealer of JK, JSW, Ultratech & Ramco cement with years of experience."
  keywords="about Goan Traders, cement dealer history, building materials supplier goa, jk cement authorized dealer, jsw cement dealer, trusted cement supplier"
>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="about-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <h1>About Goan Traders</h1>
          <p>Your trusted partner in construction since years, delivering quality building materials across Goa</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- About Content -->
    <section class="about-content">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="content-grid">
          <div class="text-content">
            <h2>Building Goa, One Project at a Time</h2>
            <p>
              Goan Traders has been serving the construction industry in Goa for years, 
              establishing ourselves as the most trusted name in building materials supply. 
              What started as a small family business has grown into Goa's leading supplier 
              of premium cement, sand, and construction materials.
            </p>
            <p>
              We take pride in being authorized dealers for India's top cement brands 
              including JK Cement, JSW Cement, Ultratech, and Ramco. Our commitment to 
              quality, competitive pricing, and exceptional customer service has made us 
              the preferred choice for contractors, builders, and homeowners across Goa.
            </p>
            <p>
              From small residential projects to large commercial constructions, we have 
              the expertise, inventory, and logistics to meet all your building material 
              needs. Our deep understanding of local construction requirements and climate 
              conditions ensures that we recommend the right products for your specific projects.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="image-content">
            <img src="/media/about1.jpg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=600&h=800" alt="Goan Traders cement warehouse and building materials storage facility" loading="lazy">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Values Section -->
    <section class="values-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Core Values</h2>
        <div class="values-grid">
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="48" height="48">
                <path fill="currentColor" d="M12 1L3 5V11C3 16.55 6.84 21.74 12 23C17.16 21.74 21 16.55 21 11V5L12 1M12 7C13.11 7 14 7.89 14 9C14 10.11 13.11 11 12 11C10.89 11 10 10.11 10 9C10 7.89 10.89 7 12 7M12 13C13.67 13 15 13.9 15 15V16H9V15C9 13.9 10.33 13 12 13Z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Trust & Reliability</h3>
            <p>Built on years of honest dealings and consistent quality delivery, earning the trust of thousands of customers across Goa.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="48" height="48">
                <path fill="currentColor" d="M12,2A7,7 0 0,1 19,9C19,11.38 17.81,13.47 16,14.74V17A1,1 0 0,1 15,18H9A1,1 0 0,1 8,17V14.74C6.19,13.47 5,11.38 5,9A7,7 0 0,1 12,2M9,21V20H15V21A1,1 0 0,1 14,22H10A1,1 0 0,1 9,21M12,4A5,5 0 0,0 7,9C7,11 8.68,12.65 10.5,12.91V16H13.5V12.91C15.32,12.65 17,11 17,9A5,5 0 0,0 12,4Z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Quality Assurance</h3>
            <p>We source only from authorized manufacturers and maintain strict quality checks to ensure every product meets industry standards.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="48" height="48">
                <path fill="currentColor" d="M13,9V3.5L18.5,9M6,2C4.89,2 4,2.89 4,4V20A2,2 0 0,0 6,22H18A2,2 0 0,0 20,20V8L14,2H6Z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Fast Delivery</h3>
            <p>With our strategic location and efficient logistics network, we ensure prompt delivery to construction sites across Goa.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="center-card-container">
          <div class="value-card">
            <div class="value-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="48" height="48">
                <path fill="currentColor" d="M13,9V3.5L18.5,9M6,2C4.89,2 4,2.89 4,4V20A2,2 0 0,0 6,22H18A2,2 0 0,0 20,20V8L14,2H6Z"/>
              </svg>
