            <div class="feature-number">01</div>
            <h3>Extensive Experience</h3>
            <p>Years of expertise in Goa's construction industry with deep understanding of local requirements and climate conditions.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="feature-card">
            <div class="feature-number">02</div>
            <h3>Complete Inventory</h3>
            <p>Comprehensive stock of all construction materials including cement, sand, aggregates, and building blocks.</p>
          </div>
          
