            </div>
            <h3>JK Cement</h3>
            <p>Premium white and grey cement with superior strength and durability for all construction needs.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="brand-card">
            <div class="brand-logo">
              <img src="/media/jswlogo.png?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=200&h=200" alt="JSW Cement dealer Goa - GGBS cement supplier" loading="lazy" style="object-fit: contain;">
            </div>
            <h3>JSW Cement</h3>
            <p>Advanced GGBS technology cement providing enhanced durability and eco-friendly construction solutions.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="brand-card">
            <div class="brand-logo">
              <img src="/media/ultratech-cement-logo.png?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=200&h=200" alt="Ultratech Cement supplier Goa - India's largest cement company" loading="lazy" style="object-fit: contain;">
            </div>
            <h3>Ultratech Cement</h3>
            <p>India's largest cement company offering consistent quality and comprehensive range of cement products.</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="brand-card">
            <div class="brand-logo">
              <img src="/media/ramco-logo.jpg" alt="Ramco Cement dealer Goa - Premium quality cement" loading="lazy" style="object-fit: contain;">
            </div>
            <h3>Ramco Cement</h3>
            <p>Trusted brand known for exceptional compressive strength and weather-resistant properties.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Leadership Section -->
    <section class="leadership-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Our Commitment</h2>
        <div class="leadership-content">
          <div class="commitment-text">
            <h3>Building Trust, Delivering Excellence</h3>
            <p>
              At Goan Traders, we believe that every construction project deserves the finest materials 
              and most reliable service. Our commitment goes beyond just supplying cement and building 
              materials - we're your partners in creating lasting structures that stand the test of time.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our team of experienced professionals understands the unique challenges of construction 
              in Goa's coastal environment. From monsoon-resistant solutions to high-humidity tolerant 
              materials, we ensure your projects are built to last.
            </p>
            <div class="commitment-points">
              <div class="point">
                <span class="checkmark">✓</span>
                Quality assurance on every delivery
              </div>
              <div class="point">
                <span class="checkmark">✓</span>
                Technical support and consultation
              </div>
              <div class="point">
                <span class="checkmark">✓</span>
                Sustainable construction solutions
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="commitment-image">
            <div class="image-placeholder">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="80" height="80">
                <path fill="#2563EB" d="M12,2A2,2 0 0,1 14,4C14,4.74 13.6,5.39 13,5.73V7H14A7,7 0 0,1 21,14H22A1,1 0 0,1 23,15V18A1,1 0 0,1 22,19H21V20A2,2 0 0,1 19,22H5A2,2 0 0,1 3,20V19H2A1,1 0 0,1 1,18V15A1,1 0 0,1 2,14H3A7,7 0 0,1 10,7H11V5.73C10.4,5.39 10,4.74 10,4A2,2 0 0,1 12,2M7.5,13A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 5,15.5A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 7.5,18A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 10,15.5A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 7.5,13M16.5,13A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 14,15.5A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 16.5,18A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 19,15.5A2.5,2.5 0 0,0 16.5,13Z"/>
              </svg>
              <p>Excellence in Every Delivery</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <h2>Ready to Start Your Construction Project?</h2>
          <p>Partner with Goa's most trusted building materials supplier for your next project</p>
          <div class="cta-buttons">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Quote Today</a>
            <a href="tel:+919765664489" class="btn btn-secondary">Call Now</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

